OL,3,CAlleged small boat pilot charged over
OL,4,Cdeaths of four migrants in Channel
OL,6,FThe alleged pilot of a small boat has
OL,7,Fbeen charged over the deaths of four
OL,8,Fmigrants who drowned trying to cross
OL,9,Fthe Channel.
OL,11,FSudanese national Alnour Mohamed Ali
OL,12,Fhas been charged with endangering life
OL,13,Fafter two men and two women died
OL,14,Ftrying to board a small boat crossing
OL,15,Fthe English Channel on Thursday, the
OL,16,FNational Crime Agency said.
OL,18,FThe 27-year-old is alleged to have
OL,19,Fpiloted the boat from France to the UK.
