OL,3,CAlleged small boat pilot charged over
OL,4,Cdeaths of four migrants in Channel
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FTwo men and two women died as they
OL,12,Fattempted to climb onto a so-called
OL,13,F"taxi boat" at Equihen-Plage, near
OL,14,FBoulogne-sur-Mer, on Thursday morning.
OL,16,F38 people were returned to the French
OL,17,Fshore after the incident south of
OL,18,FBoulogne-sur-Mer near Calais, but 74
OL,19,Fmigrants travelled on to the UK.
